        "text": "### 🏆 Winner: Hg²⁺ — by an enormous margin\n\n**Hg²⁺** has the highest affinity for thiocyanate, with log K₁ ≈ **17.47** — roughly **16 orders of magnitude** stronger than Pb²⁺ (log K₁ ≈ 0.78) and **~16 log units** above Cd²⁺ (log K₁ ≈ 1.40).",
